{"tid":2102363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有女朋友時學習一個人","createTime":"2020-07-10T11:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T10:05:15.000Z","uid":50800,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a453f484ba4b006acb503a419e7a6bda7d89bb43","tid":2102363,"uid":50800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:50:14.000Z","msg":"事源我一直有個穩定女朋友拍左幾年。佢最近工作變到好忙，我相對地好多時間。<br />\n<br />\n我本身係自住，收工返到屋企就係一個人，當佢忙時我又好多時間一個人係屋企，我就唔知做乜好。<br />\n時間一多，有時又會亂諗野，亦都有一剎那想上網搵人傾，但來來去去都係交友app，我又怕自己會做錯事。但我對其他野又提唔起勁去做咁。<br />\n<br />\n想問下究竟一個人無野做，應該點去用啲時間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503f49c7929f234dc04be8ec162f3dd1ee4dc21d","tid":2102363,"uid":361025,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55164e424a72593f255baeb3102274bac95794bc","tid":2102363,"uid":292091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:51:55.000Z","msg":"Gym"},{"pid":"5368b368fc39f94339ff6ab20e341dfbdd2ae1ae","tid":2102363,"uid":361025,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab0e25d7e4db7966b7c24bc1cae1d7bc7515cbcf","tid":2102363,"uid":361025,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:52:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"630027fd7f93d423f85e9d014b4adc5eadd188be","tid":2102363,"uid":173480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"搵我傾得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日都好易亂諗嘢"},{"pid":"2d6e71e1030f7c0d5a2d65268335a8edc09cadf5","tid":2102363,"uid":50800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"503f49c7929f234dc04be8ec162f3dd1ee4dc21d","tid":2102363,"uid":361025,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"以前都有跑步，而家肺炎，好少出去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2755e38e0307fcbe4bccb0805b6fb0650a9e4e","tid":2102363,"uid":50800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5368b368fc39f94339ff6ab20e341dfbdd2ae1ae","tid":2102363,"uid":361025,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"佢唔係成日得閒，我總有好多時間係一個人。"},{"pid":"dbbf00f2144825a1b27f110052c1ba30abcea079","tid":2102363,"uid":50800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab0e25d7e4db7966b7c24bc1cae1d7bc7515cbcf","tid":2102363,"uid":361025,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:52:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"唔敢養寵物，好怕佢離開嗰一下嘅感覺"},{"pid":"dd38b33faa5a860a86216b8f61632c2e0c8bb4ab","tid":2102363,"uid":50800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"630027fd7f93d423f85e9d014b4adc5eadd188be","tid":2102363,"uid":173480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"搵我傾得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日都好易亂諗嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:55:35.000Z","msg":"你又係一個人好易亂諗野？<br />\n情緒真係話黎就黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a531e370b9a369885174b629d14e641e06ae71a","tid":2102363,"uid":143211,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:56:10.000Z","msg":"學外語 學煮餸 學樂器 學車 學念力打飛機"},{"pid":"e2ca2a395bbf3bd66778c9cd05c1aa41af09f911","tid":2102363,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔做下運動<br />\n<br />\n打機呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再唔係多d 返屋企食飯"},{"pid":"a738e5c2cbe58b2f33bfc0f440fc4f9483b92bb4","tid":2102363,"uid":50800,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1a531e370b9a369885174b629d14e641e06ae71a","tid":2102363,"uid":143211,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:56:10.000Z","msg":"學外語 學煮餸 學樂器 學車 學念力打飛機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"外語無乜動力，因為唔會就會忘記<br />\n已經精通煮送，只係一個人完全無動力搞場大龍鳳去煮<br />\n學緊吉他，但每日只係練一個鐘就手指痛<br />\n就快十年牌了<br />\n唔用念力，差唔多日日都打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3628cff4016ccfd4eea43814d87b4bae7de9a0dc","tid":2102363,"uid":156818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"再唔係既 搵下game玩囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1c7f77e344b9780519d235eeb42b5f392eea29","tid":2102363,"uid":50800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2ca2a395bbf3bd66778c9cd05c1aa41af09f911","tid":2102363,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔做下運動<br />\n<br />\n打機呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再唔係多d 返屋企食飯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"有係屋企舉下啞鈴，仲買左ringfit玩，但好多時一個人完全無動力去做<br />\n<br />\n打機都係要有啱嘅game先玩到，跟住埋頭玩幾日打爆左又好空虛<br />\n<br />\n每星期番兩日阿媽度食飯，但一食完返到屋企又唔知做乜好"},{"pid":"37350fd6a6d7e67881355f814ef2cd1f05070380","tid":2102363,"uid":172306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"一個人都不知幾正"},{"pid":"e9d25d9455120f4c3f6dffb7816465a5dfecdc89","tid":2102363,"uid":50800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote